Spinning Fire Kick -- Down, Up + Fire.
Speed Attack -- Back, Forward + Fire.
Spinning Fire B-Ball -- Down, Down/Back, Back + Fire.
Head Spring Kick -- Back, Down/Forward, Down + Fire.


